        {
            "id": 6434771,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 大眾控(3701)急拉4.18%報67.4元，成交2,784張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大眾控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3701:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3701\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3701-TW</a>)近5分K漲速4.18%，28日11:04報67.4元，成交2,784張，今日漲幅為5.15％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>大眾控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3701:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3701\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3701-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌4.61%    ，所屬產業為電腦及週邊設備業，相關電腦週邊        上漲        4.99%。集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>        上漲        7.19%，        短期股價無明顯表現    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-468 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-194 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-228 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-46 張</li> <li>融資增減：-711 張</li> <li>融券增減：-33 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6434771",
